The paper deals with natural language processing tasks such as key phrase extraction and question generation, which are commonly studied in the sub-fields of computational linguistics (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper involves information retrieval (cs.IR) techniques for selecting candidate answers from a document, and neural networks (cs.NE) for modeling the key phrase extraction and question generation tasks.
